WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:04.000
ST-Firm inawasilisha.

00:04.000 --> 00:08.000
Jenga… jenga… Inaendeshwa na SSOS.

00:08.000 --> 00:12.000
Jifunze. Jenga. Shiriki. Wezesha.

00:12.000 --> 00:22.000
Ravine hadi Duniani! Twende pamoja!
Wanachama 29 wanaoshiriki mtandaoni.

00:22.000 --> 00:33.000
Dunia hadi Ravine! Tunajenga!
Kenya hadi Deutschland—kuvuka mipaka!

00:33.000 --> 00:45.000
Nilibeba ndoto, notebook na laptop.
Safari ikaanza Mombasa.

00:45.000 --> 00:58.000
Akademie inafungua milango. SSOS inaweka akili kwa vitendo.
SCOF inaunganisha shamba na dunia. Tunajenga kwa vizazi vijavyo.

00:58.000 --> 01:05.000
Taking Ravine to the World
and bringing the World to Eldama Ravine.

01:05.000 --> 01:10.000
Engineer Saigut Julius Kipkorir—AKA KingKunta.
